    <h1>Dokumentacja modeli danych CoffeeAppMvc5</h1>
    <p>Ostatnia aktualizacja: <span id="update-date">10 listopada 2023</span></p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Diagram relacji encji</h2>
        <div class="diagram">
            <pre>
+-------------+       +-------------+       +-------------+
|   Country   |1    *|    City     |1    *|   Roaster   |
+-------------+       +-------------+       +-------------+
      |1                                           |1
      |*                                           |*
+-------------+                              +-------------+
| CoffeeBean  |                              |   Coffee    |
+-------------+                              +-------------+
            \____________________________________/ 1
                                              *</pre>
            <p>Klucz do diagramu:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>1 - relacja jeden (jeden kraj ma wiele miast)</li>
                <li>* - relacja wiele (wiele kaw może pochodzić z jednej palarni)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>ApplicationDbContext</h2>
        <div class="model-box">
            <h3>Połączenie z bazą danych</h3>
            <p><strong>Connection String:</strong> "DefaultConnection"</p>
            
            <h3>Zestawy danych (DbSet)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Countries:</strong> DbSet&lt;Country&gt;</li>
                <li><strong>Cities:</strong> DbSet&lt;City&gt;</li>
                <li><strong>CoffeeBeans:</strong> DbSet&lt;CoffeeBean&gt;</li>
                <li><strong>Roasters:</strong> DbSet&lt;Roaster&gt;</li>
                <li><strong>Coffees:</strong> DbSet&lt;Coffee&gt;</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Konfiguracja relacji w OnModelCreating</h3>
            <table>
                <tr><th>Relacja</th><th>Typ</th><th>Kaskadowe usuwanie</th></tr>
                <tr><td>Country → Cities</td><td>1-do-wielu</td><td>Tak</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Country → CoffeeBeans</td><td>1-do-wielu</td><td>Tak</td></tr>
                <tr><td>City → Roasters</td><td>1-do-wielu</td><td>Tak</td></tr>
                <tr><td>CoffeeBean → Coffees</td><td>1-do-wielu</td><td>Nie</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Roaster → Coffees</td><td>1-do-wielu</td><td>Nie</td></tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Szczegóły modeli</h2>

        <div class="model-box">
            <h3>Country (Kraj)</h3>
            <div class="property">
                <span class="prop-name">Id</span>: <span class="prop-type">int</span>
                <div class="prop-attr">[Key]</div>
            </div>
            <div class="property">
                <span class="prop-name">Name</span>: <span class="prop-type">string</span>
                <div class="prop-attr">[Required], [StringLength(100)], [Display(Name = "Nazwa Kraju")]</div>
            </div>
            <div class="relation">
                <strong>Relacje:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Cities</strong>: ICollection&lt;City&gt; (1-do-wielu)</li>
                    <li><strong>CoffeeBeans</strong>: ICollection&lt;CoffeeBean&gt; (1-do-wielu)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="model-box">
            <h3>City (Miasto)</h3>
            <div class="property">
                <span class="prop-name">Id</span>: <span class="prop-type">int</span>
                <div class="prop-attr">[Key]</div>
            </div>
            <div class="property">
                <span class="prop-name">Name</span>: <span class="prop-type">string</span>
                <div class="prop-attr">[Required], [StringLength(100)], [Display(Name = "Nazwa Miasta")]</div>
            </div>
            <div class="property">
                <span class="prop-name">CountryId</span>: <span class="prop-type">int</span>
